author: Jaden Williams
description:
Wishlist Now! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/4167960?beta=0

The city’s under curfew after a series of disappearances and murders. You’re a young delivery driver trying to finish your gig before 9:00 PM. Set inside a decaying apartment complex, every knock on a door brings you closer to uncovering what lurks within its halls, where every delivery could be your last. The Stalking Stairs is a PSX-style psychological horror thriller featuring tense atmosphere, immersive sound design, and full voice acting.
